                    <span>As a Microsoft Certified Trainer focused on teaching SQL Server, my students are always asking, "What's *one* really good SQL book?" I will definitely recommend SQL Server_Essential Reference to my classes; it offers insight and perspective to both the relative newbie and those farther along.</span>
                  
              
